latestIgtvVideos.title: 1 Basic Kurti 🧡 6 looks
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A basic kurti , we all have one or more in our wardrobe.
If you ask me I have a bag full of kurti I didn’t wear for months . But I love to wear them , selected this orange kurti , this one I got stitched from a local shop and one of my fav 😍 Styled it into 5 looks but it can be style in more looks cuz of its solid colour .
When ever u buy a kurti try to get them in solid colours even it u love prints , as they can be styled with everything 💯
.
Tell me the look you loved the most ?😍
.
.
